<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="no">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Misfits — Launching Soon</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Misfits er på vei. En moderne coming soon-side for klesmerket med mørk editorial vibe og e-postregistrering." />
  <meta property="og:title" content="Misfits — Launching Soon" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Et nytt klesunivers er på vei. Meld deg på for tidlig tilgang." />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://api.fontshare.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://api.fontshare.com/v2/css?f[]=general-sans@400,500,600,700&f[]=cabinet-grotesk@500,700,800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    :root, [data-theme="light"] {
      --text-xs: clamp(0.75rem, 0.7rem + 0.25vw, 0.875rem);
      --text-sm: clamp(0.875rem, 0.8rem + 0.35vw, 1rem);
      --text-base: clamp(1rem, 0.95rem + 0.25vw, 1.125rem);
      --text-lg: clamp(1.125rem, 1rem + 0.75vw, 1.5rem);
      --text-xl: clamp(1.5rem, 1.2rem + 1.25vw, 2.25rem);
      --text-2xl: clamp(2rem, 1.2rem + 2.5vw, 3.5rem);
      --text-3xl: clamp(2.5rem, 1rem + 4vw, 5rem);
      --text-hero: clamp(3.5rem, 1.2rem + 7vw, 8rem);

      --space-1: 0.25rem;
      --space-2: 0.5rem;
      --space-3: 0.75rem;
      --space-4: 1rem;
      --space-5: 1.25rem;
      --space-6: 1.5rem;
      --space-8: 2rem;
      --space-10: 2.5rem;
      --space-12: 3rem;
      --space-16: 4rem;
      --space-20: 5rem;
      --space-24: 6rem;
      --space-32: 8rem;

      --color-bg: #f5f2ec;
      --color-surface: #faf7f2;
      --color-surface-2: #ffffff;
      --color-surface-offset: #ede8df;
      --color-border: rgba(29, 26, 22, 0.12);
      --color-divider: rgba(29, 26, 22, 0.08);
      --color-text: #171411;
      --color-text-muted: #6f6a63;
      --color-text-faint: #9a948c;
      --color-text-inverse: #f7f4ee;
      --color-primary: #8cff6a;
      --color-primary-hover: #74ea51;
      --color-primary-active: #5cc83d;
      --color-primary-highlight: rgba(140,255,106,0.18);
      --radius-sm: 0.375rem;
      --radius-md: 0.75rem;
      --radius-lg: 1rem;
      --radius-xl: 1.5rem;
      --radius-full: 9999px;
      --shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      --shadow-md: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
      --shadow-lg: 0 24px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.16);
      --content-default: 1120px;
      --font-display: 'Cabinet Grotesk', 'Arial Narrow', sans-serif;
      --font-body: 'General Sans', 'Inter', sans-serif;
      --grid-line: rgba(29, 26, 22, 0.06);
      --hero-glow: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 10%, rgba(140,255,106,0.14), transparent 34%), radial-gradient(circle at 80% 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.5), transparent 26%);
    }

    [data-theme="dark"] {
      --color-bg: #090909;
      --color-surface: #111111;
      --color-surface-2: #181818;
      --color-surface-offset: #0e0e0e;
      --color-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      --color-divider: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
      --color-text: #f4f1eb;
      --color-text-muted: #a39b92;
      --color-text-faint: #6d675f;
      --color-text-inverse: #0a0a0a;
      --color-primary: #a7ff84;
      --color-primary-hover: #b8ff9a;
      --color-primary-active: #91ee69;
      --color-primary-highlight: rgba(167,255,132,0.14);
      --shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
      --shadow-md: 0 16px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
      --shadow-lg: 0 24px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.55);
      --grid-line: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      --hero-glow: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 10%, rgba(167,255,132,0.16), transparent 30%), radial-gradient(circle at 84% 12%, rgba(255,255,255,0.06), transparent 22%);
    }

    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      :root:not([data-theme]) {
        --color-bg: #090909;
        --color-surface: #111111;
        --color-surface-2: #181818;
        --color-surface-offset: #0e0e0e;
        --color-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        --color-divider: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
        --color-text: #f4f1eb;
        --color-text-muted: #a39b92;
        --color-text-faint: #6d675f;
        --color-text-inverse: #0a0a0a;
        --color-primary: #a7ff84;
        --color-primary-hover: #b8ff9a;
        --color-primary-active: #91ee69;
        --color-primary-highlight: rgba(167,255,132,0.14);
        --grid-line: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
        --hero-glow: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 10%, rgba(167,255,132,0.16), transparent 30%), radial-gradient(circle at 84% 12%, rgba(255,255,255,0.06), transparent 22%);
      }
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
      text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
    }
    body {
      min-height: 100dvh;
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: var(--text-base);
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--color-text);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, rgba(0,0,0,0.04)),
        var(--hero-glow),
        var(--color-bg);
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }
    img, svg { display: block; max-width: 100%; }
    button, input { font: inherit; }
    a, button, input {
      transition: color 180ms cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1),
                  background 180ms cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1),
                  border-color 180ms cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1),
                  transform 180ms cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1),
                  box-shadow 180ms cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
    }
    :focus-visible {
      outline: 2px solid var(--color-primary);
      outline-offset: 4px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    }
    .sr-only {
      position: absolute; width: 1px; height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: -1px;
      overflow: hidden; clip: rect(0,0,0,0); white-space: nowrap; border: 0;
    }
    .page-shell {
      position: relative;
      isolation: isolate;
    }
    .page-shell::before {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(var(--grid-line) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, var(--grid-line) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 72px 72px;
      mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, black 35%, transparent 85%);
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: -1;
    }
    .container {
      width: min(calc(100% - 2rem), var(--content-default));
      margin-inline: auto;
    }
    .skip-link {
      position: absolute;
      left: var(--space-4);
      top: -100%;
      background: var(--color-primary);
      color: var(--color-text-inverse);
      padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4);
      border-radius: var(--radius-full);
      z-index: 100;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
    }
    .skip-link:focus { top: var(--space-4); }

    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 10;
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-bg) 72%, transparent);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-divider);
    }
    .topbar {
      min-height: 76px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: var(--space-4);
    }
    .brand {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--space-3);
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
    }
    .brand-mark {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, var(--color-surface-2), var(--color-surface));
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }
    .brand-name {
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--color-text);
    }
    .header-actions {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--space-3);
    }
    .theme-toggle,
    .mini-pill {
      min-width: 44px;
      min-height: 44px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-full);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-surface) 72%, transparent);
      color: var(--color-text);
    }
    .mini-pill {
      padding: 0 var(--space-4);
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .mini-pill:hover,
    .theme-toggle:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }

    main {
      padding-block: clamp(var(--space-8), 4vw, var(--space-16));
    }
    .hero {
      min-height: calc(100dvh - 88px);
      display: grid;
      align-items: center;
      padding-block: clamp(var(--space-12), 8vw, var(--space-24));
    }
    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.1fr) minmax(280px, 0.9fr);
      gap: clamp(var(--space-8), 4vw, var(--space-16));
      align-items: end;
    }
    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--space-2);
      padding: 0.5rem 0.9rem;
      border-radius: var(--radius-full);
      background: var(--color-primary-highlight);
      border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary) 28%, var(--color-border));
      color: var(--color-text);
      font-size: var(--text-xs);
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
    }
    .eyebrow-dot {
      width: 0.5rem;
      height: 0.5rem;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--color-primary);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary) 20%, transparent);
    }
    h1 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: var(--text-hero);
      line-height: 0.92;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      max-width: 10ch;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .hero-copy p {
      font-size: var(--text-lg);
      color: var(--color-text-muted);
      max-width: 34ch;
      margin-top: var(--space-5);
    }
    .hero-meta {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: var(--space-3);
      margin-top: var(--space-6);
    }
    .meta-chip {
      padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
      border-radius: var(--radius-full);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-surface) 82%, transparent);
      color: var(--color-text-muted);
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
    }
    .hero-card {
      position: relative;
      padding: clamp(var(--space-6), 3.5vw, var(--space-8));
      border-radius: 28px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-surface-2) 72%, transparent), color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-surface) 90%, transparent));
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: auto -10% -20% auto;
      width: 240px;
      aspect-ratio: 1;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary) 30%, transparent), transparent 68%);
      filter: blur(4px);
    }
    .stack {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--space-4);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    }
    .launch-date {
      display: grid;
      gap: var(--space-2);
    }
    .label {
      color: var(--color-text-faint);
      font-size: var(--text-xs);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    }
    .launch-date strong {
      font-size: var(--text-xl);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }
    .stat-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: var(--space-3);
      margin-block: var(--space-6);
    }
    .stat {
      padding: var(--space-4);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-surface) 90%, transparent);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-divider);
    }
    .stat strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: var(--text-lg);
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
    }
    .stat span {
      color: var(--color-text-muted);
      font-size: var(--text-xs);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    }
    .newsletter {
      display: grid;
      gap: var(--space-3);
      margin-top: var(--space-5);
    }
    .input-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
      gap: var(--space-3);
    }
    .input-row input {
      min-height: 54px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-full);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      padding: 0 var(--space-5);
      background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-bg) 55%, var(--color-surface-2));
      color: var(--color-text);
    }
    .input-row input::placeholder { color: var(--color-text-faint); }
    .cta {
      min-height: 54px;
      padding: 0 var(--space-5);
      border-radius: var(--radius-full);
      border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary) 20%, transparent);
      background: var(--color-primary);
      color: var(--color-text-inverse);
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary) 22%, transparent);
    }
    .cta:hover {
      background: var(--color-primary-hover);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }
    .fineprint {
      color: var(--color-text-faint);
      font-size: var(--text-xs);
      max-width: 40ch;
    }
    .success-note {
      display: none;
      padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      background: var(--color-primary-highlight);
      border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary) 24%, var(--color-border));
      color: var(--color-text);
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
    }
    .success-note.is-visible { display: block; }

    .info-strip {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--color-divider);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-divider);
      padding-block: var(--space-5);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .marquee {
      display: flex;
      gap: var(--space-8);
      white-space: nowrap;
      color: var(--color-text-muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      font-size: var(--text-xs);
      animation: drift 22s linear infinite;
      width: max-content;
    }
    @keyframes drift {
      from { transform: translateX(0); }
      to { transform: translateX(-50%); }
    }

    .section {
      padding-block: clamp(var(--space-12), 8vw, var(--space-24));
    }
    .section-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.75fr 1.25fr;
      gap: clamp(var(--space-6), 4vw, var(--space-12));
      align-items: start;
    }
    .section-kicker {
      color: var(--color-text-faint);
      font-size: var(--text-xs);
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    }
    .section h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: var(--text-2xl);
      line-height: 0.98;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      max-width: 11ch;
    }
    .section-intro {
      color: var(--color-text-muted);
      max-width: 48ch;
      margin-top: var(--space-4);
    }
    .feature-layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 0.85fr;
      gap: var(--space-4);
      margin-top: var(--space-2);
    }
    .feature-card,
    .quote-card,
    .details-card {
      position: relative;
      border-radius: 28px;
      background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-surface) 84%, transparent);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .feature-card {
      padding: clamp(var(--space-6), 3vw, var(--space-8));
      min-height: 420px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.2) 100%),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary) 26%, transparent), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(145deg, color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-surface-2) 92%, transparent), color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-surface-offset) 88%, transparent));
    }
    .feature-card::after {
      content: "MISFITS";
      position: absolute;
      top: var(--space-5);
      right: var(--space-5);
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 5rem);
      line-height: 0.9;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.08em;
      color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-text) 8%, transparent);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .feature-card .tag {
      display: inline-flex;
      width: fit-content;
      padding: 0.55rem 0.85rem;
      border-radius: var(--radius-full);
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.28);
      color: #f7f4ee;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      font-size: var(--text-xs);
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      margin-bottom: auto;
    }
    .feature-card h3,
    .details-card h3,
    .quote-card h3 {
      font-size: var(--text-xl);
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .feature-card p,
    .details-card p,
    .quote-card p { color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-top: var(--space-3); }
    .side-stack {
      display: grid;
      gap: var(--space-4);
    }
    .quote-card,
    .details-card { padding: clamp(var(--space-5), 2.5vw, var(--space-6)); }
    .quote-card blockquote {
      font-size: var(--text-lg);
      line-height: 1.35;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      max-width: 22ch;
    }
    .quote-card footer {
      margin-top: var(--space-5);
      color: var(--color-text-faint);
      font-size: var(--text-xs);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    }

    .countdown {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: var(--space-4);
      margin-top: var(--space-6);
    }
    .countdown-tile {
      padding: var(--space-5);
      border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
      background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-surface) 85%, transparent);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .countdown-tile strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      letter-spacing: -0.06em;
      line-height: 0.95;
    }
    .countdown-tile span {
      color: var(--color-text-faint);
      font-size: var(--text-xs);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    }

    footer {
      padding-bottom: var(--space-10);
    }
    .footer-card {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: var(--space-4);
      padding: var(--space-5);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-divider);
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-surface) 75%, transparent);
    }
    .footer-card p {
      color: var(--color-text-muted);
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
    }

    [data-reveal] {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(22px);
      transition: opacity 700ms cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1), transform 700ms cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1);
    }
    [data-reveal].is-visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .hero-grid,
      .section-grid,
      .feature-layout {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      h1 { max-width: 8ch; }
      .hero-card { max-width: 680px; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .topbar { min-height: 68px; }
      .brand-name { letter-spacing: 0.16em; }
      .mini-pill { display: none; }
      .input-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .stat-grid,
      .countdown { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
      .footer-card {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 460px) {
      .container { width: min(calc(100% - 1.25rem), var(--content-default)); }
      h1 { font-size: clamp(3rem, 16vw, 4.75rem); }
      .hero-copy p { font-size: var(--text-base); }
      .stat-grid,
      .countdown { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--space-3); }
      .countdown-tile,
      .stat { padding: var(--space-4); }
    }

    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      *, *::before, *::after {
        animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
        animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
        transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
        scroll-behavior: auto !important;
      }
      [data-reveal] { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <a class="skip-link" href="#main">Hopp til innhold</a>
  <div class="page-shell">
    <header>
      <div class="container topbar">
        <a class="brand" href="#top" aria-label="Misfits hjem">
          <span class="brand-mark" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-label="Misfits logo">
              <path d="M10 44L24 18L32 32L40 18L54 44" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <path d="M18 44H46" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <span class="brand-name">Misfits</span>
        </a>
        <div class="header-actions">
          <a class="mini-pill" href="#notify">Tidlig tilgang</a>
          <button class="theme-toggle" type="button" data-theme-toggle aria-label="Bytt tema">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M21 12.79A9 9 0 1 1 11.21 3 7 7 0 0 0 21 12.79z"/>
            </svg>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main id="main">
      <section class="hero container" id="top">
        <div class="hero-grid">
          <div class="hero-copy" data-reveal>
            <div class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow-dot"></span>Launching soon</div>
            <h1>For the ones who never fit in.</h1>
            <p>Misfits bygger et mørkt, moderne klesunivers med editorial attitude, skarpe silhuetter og limited drops. Første release nærmer seg.</p>
            <div class="hero-meta" aria-label="Høydepunkter">
              <span class="meta-chip">Streetwear / Elevated basics</span>
              <span class="meta-chip">Limited first drop</span>
              <span class="meta-chip">Early access list</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <aside class="hero-card" id="notify" data-reveal>
            <div class="stack">
              <div class="brand-mark" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M10 44L24 18L32 32L40 18L54 44" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                  <path d="M18 44H46" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="launch-date">
                <span class="label">Drop status</span>
                <strong>Season 01 incoming</strong>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="stat-grid" aria-label="Merkeøyeblikk">
              <div class="stat"><strong>01</strong><span>First collection</span></div>
              <div class="stat"><strong>24/7</strong><span>On the radar</span></div>
              <div class="stat"><strong>Low qty</strong><span>Exclusive drop</span></div>
            </div>

            <form class="newsletter" id="signup-form">
              <label class="label" for="email">Få beskjed når vi går live</label>
              <div class="input-row">
                <input id="email" name="email" type="email" placeholder="din@epost.no" autocomplete="email" required />
                <button class="cta" type="submit">Notify me</button>
              </div>
              <p class="fineprint">Kun lanseringsnyheter, early access og første drop. Ingen spam.</p>
              <p class="success-note" id="success-note" aria-live="polite">Du er på listen. Misfits sender signal når droppet er klart.</p>
            </form>
          </aside>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="info-strip" aria-label="Merkeinformasjonsstripe">
        <div class="marquee">
          <span>Misfits</span><span>Launching Soon</span><span>Limited Drop</span><span>Built for outsiders</span><span>Misfits</span><span>Launching Soon</span><span>Limited Drop</span><span>Built for outsiders</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section container">
        <div class="section-grid">
          <div data-reveal>
            <p class="section-kicker">Brand direction</p>
            <h2>Raw edge. Clean silhouette.</h2>
            <p class="section-intro">Uttrykket er enkelt, men ikke trygt. Misfits balanserer monokrome toner, sterke detaljer og en launch-først identitet som føles eksklusiv før første plagg er ute.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-layout" data-reveal>
            <article class="feature-card">
              <span class="tag">Coming soon</span>
              <h3>Engineered for the first impression.</h3>
              <p>En hero-opplevelse med mørk editorial stemning, tydelig launch-fokus og nok attitude til at merket føles levende før nettbutikken åpner.</p>
            </article>
            <div class="side-stack">
              <article class="quote-card">
                <h3>Brand note</h3>
                <blockquote>“Not made to blend in. Made for the ones who move differently.”</blockquote>
                <footer>Misfits manifesto</footer>
              </article>
              <article class="details-card">
                <h3>What's next</h3>
                <p>Lanseringssiden kan enkelt bygges videre med lookbook, produktgrid, countdown til drop og integrasjon mot nyhetsbrev eller Shopify.</p>
              </article>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section container">
        <div data-reveal>
          <p class="section-kicker">Countdown</p>
          <h2>Almost on the street.</h2>
          <p class="section-intro">Nedtellingen er satt til en demo-lansering 30 dager frem i tid. Den kan endres til eksakt dato når dere bestemmer drop-dagen.</p>
          <div class="countdown" aria-label="Nedtelling til lansering">
            <div class="countdown-tile"><strong id="days">30</strong><span>Dager</span></div>
            <div class="countdown-tile"><strong id="hours">00</strong><span>Timer</span></div>
            <div class="countdown-tile"><strong id="minutes">00</strong><span>Minutter</span></div>
            <div class="countdown-tile"><strong id="seconds">00</strong><span>Sekunder</span></div>
          </div>
